        <button class="btn-block" style="margin-top:0" onclick="nextPost()">Continuer →</button>
      </div>`;
  } else if(postStep===4){
    c.innerHTML=`
      <div style="margin-bottom:16px;font-size:0.84rem;color:var(--ink3)">Choisissez comment booster votre annonce :</div>
